parameters.name: DeletionStrategy
parameters.description:
The deletion policy. The policy is used to manage synchronized users when you delete the RAM user provisioning. Valid values:

*   Delete: When you delete the RAM user provisioning, the system deletes the synchronized users.
*   Keep: When you delete the RAM user provisioning, the system retains the synchronized users.

>  If you do not specify this parameter, the deletion policy that is configured when you create the RAM user provisioning is used.

parameters.name: DirectoryId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource directory.

parameters.name: UserProvisioningId
parameters.description: The ID of the RAM user provisioning.
